Table 12.   Justice system expenditures of 68 large county governments by activity,
Notes:  Fiscal years end between July 1997 and June 1998.
Jurisdictions without data did not report for 1998.
a/ In 1997 Middlesex County in Massachusetts was abolished.  Thus it is no longer being included in this table.
The county taking its place among the 68 large counties in this table is DeKalb, Georgia.
